<B=L>Accept
& Accept &
    _                      _   
   / \   ___ ___ ___ _ __ | |_ 
  / _ \ / __/ __/ _ \ '_ \| __|
 / ___ \ (_| (_|  __/ |_) | |_ 
/_/   \_\___\___\___| .__/ \__|
