<B=16>Attribution-Reporting-Register-Trigger
& Attribution-Reporting-Register-Trigger &
    _   _   _        _ _           _   _                   ____            
   / \ | |_| |_ _ __(_) |__  _   _| |_(_) ___  _ __       |  _ \ ___ _ __  
  / _ \| __| __| '__| | '_ \| | | | __| |/ _ \| '_ \ _____| |_) / _ \ '_ \ 
 / ___ \ |_| |_| |  | | |_) | |_| | |_| | (_) | | | |_____|  _ <  __/ |_) |
/_/   \_\__|\__|_|  |_|_.__/ \__,_|\__|_|\___/|_| |_|     |_| \_\___| .__/ 
                                                                    |_|    
            _   _                   ____            _     _                 
  ___  _ __| |_(_)_ __   __ _      |  _ \ ___  __ _(_)___| |_ ___ _ __      
 / _ \| '__| __| | '_ \ / _` |_____| |_) / _ \/ _` | / __| __/ _ \ '__|____ 
| (_) | |  | |_| | | | | (_| |_____|  _ <  __/ (_| | \__ \ ||  __/ | |_____|
 \___/|_|   \__|_|_| |_|\__, |     |_| \_\___|\__, |_|___/\__\___|_|        
                        |___/                 |___/                         
 _____     _                       
|_   _| __(_) __ _  __ _  ___ _ __ 
  | || '__| |/ _` |/ _` |/ _ \ '__|
  | || |  | | (_| | (_| |  __/ |   
