<B=3F>Sec-WebSocket-Key
& Sec-WebSocket-Key &
 ____              __        __   _    ____             _        _        _  __
/ ___|  ___  ___   \ \      / /__| |__/ ___|  ___   ___| | _____| |_     | |/ /
\___ \ / _ \/ __|___\ \ /\ / / _ \ '_ \___ \ / _ \ / __| |/ / _ \ __|____| ' / 
 ___) |  __/ (_|_____\ V  V /  __/ |_) |__) | (_) | (__|   <  __/ ||_____| . \ 
|____/ \___|\___|     \_/\_/ \___|_.__/____/ \___/ \___|_|\_\___|\__|    |_|\_\
                                                                               
            
  ___ _   _ 
 / _ \ | | |
