HTTP resources and specifications

HTTP was first specified in the early 1990s. Designed with extensibility in mind, it has seen numerous
additions over the years; this lead to its specification being scattered through numerous specification
documents (in the midst of experimental abandoned extensions). This page lists relevant resources about
HTTP.

