 ___) | | | | |\  |  __/ |_ \ V  V / (_) | |  |   < 
|____/|_|_| |_| \_|\___|\__| \_/\_/ \___/|_|  |_|\_\
                                                    
    _         _   _                _   _           _   _             
   / \  _   _| |_| |__   ___ _ __ | |_(_) ___ __ _| |_(_) ___  _ __  
  / _ \| | | | __| '_ \ / _ \ '_ \| __| |/ __/ _` | __| |/ _ \| '_ \ 
 / ___ \ |_| | |_| | | |  __/ | | | |_| | (_| (_| | |_| | (_) | | | |
/_/   \_\__,_|\__|_| |_|\___|_| |_|\__|_|\___\__,_|\__|_|\___/|_| |_|
                                                                     
